    seo: { title: `Hard Water in the UK: How It's Stripping Your Skin and What Actually Helps`, description: `Hard water — common across southern and central England — disrupts skin pH, strips lipids, and leaves irritating mineral residue that standard cleansers make worse. This article explains the problem…` },
