    seo: { title: `Why British Skin Needs More Moisture Than You Think`, description: `The UK's cloud cover, wind, and low sunshine hours leave British skin chronically moisture-deprived, often without obvious symptoms. This piece explains why the barrier — not just water intake — is…` },
