    seo: { title: `Is Ghee Skincare Suitable for All Skin Types? The Honest Answer`, description: `An honest, balanced guide to which skin types benefit most from ghee skincare — covering dry, mature, sensitive, combination, and oily skin types — with a clear-eyed note on where oleic-acid-rich…` },
