    seo: { title: `UK Tap Water vs Your Skin Barrier: What Every British Woman Should Know`, description: `Over 60% of England has hard or very hard tap water that disrupts skin pH and reacts with surfactant cleansers to leave irritating residue. This piece explains the science and makes the case for…` },
